279
00:21:42,460 --> 00:21:43,880
The CEO.

280
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:47,410
The nation's dream guy. The ladies' man. The walking pheromones.

281
00:21:47,410 --> 00:21:50,570
Royal Group's public goods. Isn't this love?

282
00:21:50,570 --> 00:21:52,540
- Of course it is.
- It definitely is.

283
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:55,180
- This is exactly what love is.
- This is exactly what love is.

284
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:59,190
You scared me to death!

285
00:21:59,190 --> 00:22:00,650
Chuchu, what are you doing?

286
00:22:00,650 --> 00:22:03,130
Sorry, my hand slipped.

287
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:05,880
Did I scare you?

288
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:09,650
I'm sorry. I'll go make copies.

289
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:17,020
