333
00:24:54,850 --> 00:24:58,300
Young ones? Who?

334
00:25:16,510 --> 00:25:18,140
Thank you! Thank you!

335
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:20,280
Thank you, Director Xu. Take care.

336
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:30,520
Uncle Hu, why do I feel that Director Xu doesn't really support me in taking over?

337
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:34,340
Don't worry.

338
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:41,600
