346
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:22,860
Before we remove her from the chairwoman position,

347
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:26,710
I have a gift to give you.

348
00:26:27,390 --> 00:26:29,310
What gift?

349
00:26:30,980 --> 00:26:36,870
Director Xu, Tianxing had to clean up the mess for the companies my sister led in the past.

350
00:26:36,870 --> 00:26:38,090
You know this better than anyone else, right?

351
00:26:38,090 --> 00:26:39,770
Uncle Hu, what do you mean by this?

352
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:41,930
Did you see last quarter's financial report?

353
00:26:41,930 --> 00:26:46,220
I'm sure everyone's well aware how far my sister's abilities extend.

354
00:26:48,330 --> 00:26:49,630
Where did you get this from?

355
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:52,200
It was on your desk when I got here this morning.

356
00:26:53,120 --> 00:26:57,930
Are they so worried that I wouldn't notice it that they put it directly in my office?

357
00:26:57,930 --> 00:27:00,810
So they clearly want to provoke me.

358
00:27:00,810 --> 00:27:02,260
It's only an audio recording, not a video recording.

359
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:04,590
It might not really be Young Master.

360
00:27:06,650 --> 00:27:08,830
It is He Tianjian.

361
00:27:09,850 --> 00:27:13,220
My dearest younger brother.

362
00:27:13,220 --> 00:27:15,710
How can I not recognize his voice?

363
00:27:21,630 --> 00:27:22,940
Bring the car.

364
00:27:22,940 --> 00:27:24,490
Yes.

365
00:27:35,340 --> 00:27:38,510
[Tianliang Sakura Shrimp Processing Plant]

366
00:28:01,460 --> 00:28:04,450
Sister, why did you come here?

367
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:11,340
Director Xu, Tianxing had to clean up the mess for the companies my sister led in the past.

368
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:13,690
You know this better than anyone else, right?

369
00:28:13,690 --> 00:28:15,540
What's the meaning of this?

370
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:19,210
Oh, you caught me!

371
00:28:19,210 --> 00:28:21,870
I'm asking you, what's the meaning of this?

372
00:28:21,870 --> 00:28:24,210
Exactly what you heard.

373
00:28:24,210 --> 00:28:27,930
