377
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:49,140
Our performance this year can't even compare to the same period last year.

378
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:52,050
Do you want to take a look yourself?

379
00:28:52,050 --> 00:28:53,660
Enough!

380
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:03,830
Don't make it sound like you can't bear to be without him.

381
00:29:03,830 --> 00:29:08,030
Wake him up now and have him make pocket money for you then!

382
00:29:08,030 --> 00:29:13,780
Sorry, this is how cruel reality is.

383
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:16,400
Yes, this is how cruel reality is.

384
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:19,570
No matter how hard you work, you can't replace He Tianxing.

385
00:29:19,570 --> 00:29:22,970
Sorry, it's so cruel!

386
00:29:22,970 --> 00:29:26,960
He Tianjian! Be careful with what you say.

387
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:29,380
Aiyo, did I say something wrong?

388
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:31,590
Fine, I won't say anything.

389
00:29:31,590 --> 00:29:35,720
But the numbers speak for themselves.

390
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:40,330
With this attitude of yours, you want to trample over me and take my spot?

391
00:29:40,330 --> 00:29:43,140
Aren't you too naive?

392
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:47,790
Sis, I don't call the shots on whether I take the position.

393
00:29:47,790 --> 00:29:50,160
It's decided by a board vote.

394
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:52,160
You should know that.

395
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:56,830
Too bad, like you just heard, everyone thinks you're not good enough.

396
00:29:58,570 --> 00:30:02,950
You haven't learned anything, but you are great at backstabbing!

397
00:30:04,930 --> 00:30:08,930
