398
00:30:08,930 --> 00:30:11,210
I hit you because you're my younger brother.

399
00:30:11,210 --> 00:30:13,690
If you weren't my brother, I would have killed you already.

400
00:30:13,690 --> 00:30:16,510
Why would I leave a traitor like you to stab me in the back?

401
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:19,430
You can't kill me, Sis.

402
00:30:19,430 --> 00:30:21,910
Can't you just accept reality?

403
00:30:21,910 --> 00:30:25,800
You'll spend your life paving the way for me.

404
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,830
It sounds kind of sad,

405
00:30:27,830 --> 00:30:32,990
but don't worry, I'll remember everything you've done for me.

406
00:30:33,780 --> 00:30:36,270
Once I officially take over,

407
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:39,850
I absolutely won't mistreat a competent stepping stone such as yourself.

408
00:30:39,850 --> 00:30:41,990
He Tianjian!

409
00:30:56,850 --> 00:30:59,870
If hitting me can relieve your anger,

410
00:30:59,870 --> 00:31:02,120
then hit me as much as you want.

411
00:31:02,120 --> 00:31:05,760
