413
00:31:08,780 --> 00:31:11,830
Otherwise, I will take Tianliang Group from your hands very soon.

414
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:13,460
Don't think that I won't dare.

415
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:16,700
