416
00:31:16,700 --> 00:31:18,910
That's impossible.

417
00:31:18,910 --> 00:31:20,890
You can't bear to die.

418
00:31:20,890 --> 00:31:23,530
The power struggle is too beautiful, isn't it?

419
00:31:23,530 --> 00:31:25,990
He Tianjian!

420
00:31:38,110 --> 00:31:41,590
I won't let you get away with this. Just you wait.

421
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:53,910
