427
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,430
Social media hashtags will be used to

428
00:32:18,430 --> 00:32:22,730
promote our upcoming hot spring resort chain.

429
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:26,330
Which one should I choose?

430
00:32:26,330 --> 00:32:28,900
It's such a difficult choice.

431
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:31,210
Xiao'en, help me choose.

432
00:32:31,210 --> 00:32:34,980
