452
00:33:50,170 --> 00:33:51,590
Good afternoon, Young Master.

453
00:33:51,590 --> 00:33:54,150
Qiutian, long time no see!

454
00:33:54,150 --> 00:33:56,160
You've gotten prettier.

455
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:58,840
I saw you a few days ago.

456
00:33:58,840 --> 00:34:01,240
Miss, am I that scary?

457
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:03,730
