466
00:34:31,210 --> 00:34:33,980
At a nightclub? Or a bar?

467
00:34:34,640 --> 00:34:36,980
We didn't have a one night stand, did we? Did we? Did we? Did we?

468
00:34:36,980 --> 00:34:38,870
I’m not so l—

469
00:34:38,870 --> 00:34:40,690
L...?

